SELECT 
    'CancelPurchaseDocumentLine' || '::' || "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ID"     AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"                                                     AS "PurchaseDocumentLine",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"                                                     AS "PurchaseOrderLine",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine"."DocumentCategory"                                       AS "DocumentCategory",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."Time"                                           AS "Time",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                      AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"                                  AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"
        ON "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID" = "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."ObjectID"
WHERE "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'DeletionIndicator'
    AND "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."NewValue" = 'Y'
    AND "PurchaseDocumentLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL
